      <title>美元熊抓住了崩溃的杰出主义的概念</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-02/dollar-bears-seize-on-notion-of-crumbling-us-exceptionalism</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统的关税威胁在上周再次提高了美元，但越来越多的投资者正在押注绿色背景，这表明美国经济正在降温，并担心贸易战将进一步削弱它。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-02/dollar-bears-seize-on-notion-of-crumbling-us-exceptionalism</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Mar 2025 17:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
