      <title>世界银行敦促南非削减劳动，投资繁文tape节</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-02/world-bank-urges-south-africa-to-cut-labor-investment-red-tape</link>
      <description><![CDATA[世界银行说，南非应该结束其“过度”的监管负担，并改革其黑人所有权法律，以消除困扰其经济的“瘫痪迹象”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-02/world-bank-urges-south-africa-to-cut-labor-investment-red-tape</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Mar 2025 11:02:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
